QuestionTxt: Do you think Saddam Hussein's regime in Iraq was directly involved in planning, financing, or carrying out the terrorist attacks (on the World Trade Center and the Pentagon) of September 11th, 2001, or not?
SourceDoc: Princeton Survey Research Associates International/Newsweek Poll
StudyNote: Interviewing on September 30, 2004 was limited to the Pacific and Mountain time zones after the presidential debate concluded.
